{"id":310,"date":"2019-06-08T13:58:48","date_gmt":"2019-06-08T17:58:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.torix.ca\/?page_id=310"},"modified":"2019-06-26T13:00:04","modified_gmt":"2019-06-26T17:00:04","slug":"community-projects","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.torix.ca\/community-projects\/","title":{"rendered":"Community Projects"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row row_height_percent=&#8221;0&#8243; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243;][vc_column column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; align_horizontal=&#8221;align_center&#8221; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; medium_width=&#8221;0&#8243; mobile_width=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_x=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y_down=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/6&#8243;][vc_separator sep_color=&#8221;color-uydo&#8221; icon=&#8221;fa fa-plus&#8221; icon_position=&#8221;left&#8221; css_animation=&#8221;alpha-anim&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; position_vertical=&#8221;middle&#8221; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; medium_width=&#8221;0&#8243; mobile_width=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_x=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y_down=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243; width=&#8221;5\/6&#8243;][vc_column_text text_lead=&#8221;yes&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h4>Stratum 1 NTP Cluster<\/h4>\n<p>TorIX hosts a stratum 1 NTP cluster which is globally reachable and handles 500,000 queries per minute, mostly from within North America.\u00a0 Our servers are reachable at ntp.torix.ca using IPv4 or IPv6 and we are listed as part of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ntppool.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NTP Pool Project<\/a>.\u00a0 We run multiple separate time sources for redundancy.<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong>ntp1.torix.ca<\/strong> (206.108.0.131 or 2602:fde5:2a::11)<br \/>\n<strong>ntp2.torix.ca <\/strong>(206.108.0.132 or 2602:fde5:2a::12)<br \/>\n<strong>ntp3.torix.ca<\/strong> (206.108.0.133 or 2602:fde5:2a::13)<\/p>\n<p>You are free to use our NTP servers if you wish.\u00a0 We recommend you use hostnames, if possible, rather than hard-coding the IPv4 or IPV6 addresses.\u00a0 The hostname <strong>ntp.torix.ca<\/strong> will return the above IP addresses in a round-robin fashion and this is the preferred hostname to use.<\/p>\n<p>If you are using ntpd for NTP, please consider using &#8220;pool ntp.torix.ca&#8221; rather than &#8220;server ntp.torix.ca&#8221; as the pool syntax will accept multiple IP&#8217;s from a DNS query and refresh occasionally as well, so any IP changes will not impact your NTP servers.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; align_horizontal=&#8221;align_center&#8221; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; medium_width=&#8221;0&#8243; mobile_width=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_x=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y_down=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/6&#8243;][vc_separator sep_color=&#8221;color-uydo&#8221; icon=&#8221;fa fa-plus&#8221; icon_position=&#8221;left&#8221; css_animation=&#8221;alpha-anim&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;5\/6&#8243;][vc_column_text text_lead=&#8221;yes&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h4>AS112 Project<\/h4>\n<p>We run an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.as112.net\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AS112 Project<\/a> node to help reduce the load on the global domain name system.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; align_horizontal=&#8221;align_center&#8221; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; medium_width=&#8221;0&#8243; mobile_width=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_x=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y_down=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/6&#8243;][vc_separator sep_color=&#8221;color-uydo&#8221; icon=&#8221;fa fa-plus&#8221; icon_position=&#8221;left&#8221; css_animation=&#8221;alpha-anim&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;5\/6&#8243;][vc_column_text text_lead=&#8221;yes&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h4><\/h4>\n<h4>NLNOG RING Node<\/h4>\n<p>We participate in the <a href=\"https:\/\/ring.nlnog.net\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NLNOG RING<\/a> which is exclusive to network operators and allows them to trouble-shoot and debug network issues across the world.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row row_height_percent=&#8221;0&#8243; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243;][vc_column column_width_percent=&#8221;100&#8243; align_horizontal=&#8221;align_center&#8221; overlay_alpha=&#8221;50&#8243; gutter_size=&#8221;3&#8243; medium_width=&#8221;0&#8243; mobile_width=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_x=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y=&#8221;0&#8243; shift_y_down=&#8221;0&#8243; z_index=&#8221;0&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/6&#8243;][vc_separator sep_color=&#8221;color-uydo&#8221; [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-310","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Community Projects - Toronto Internet Exchange TorIX<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-p